query:
SELECT 
  sp.id as permission_id,
  sp.userId as member_user_id,
  u.username as member_username,
  u.name as member_name,
  sp.stockUserId as stock_user_id,
  su.name as stock_user_name,
  su.initialBalance,
  sp.startAmount,
  sp.profitPercentage,
  sp.deposit
FROM stockUserPermissions sp
LEFT JOIN users u ON sp.userId = u.id
LEFT JOIN stockUsers su ON sp.stockUserId = su.id
ORDER BY sp.id;
